<section id="idg-osoperator-shared-appendix-r-confsettings-metrics-xml-1">
 <title>Configuration Settings for the Metrics Agent</title>
 <para>
  The configuration settings for the Metrics Agent are provided in the
  following file:
 </para>
 <para>
  <literal>/etc/monasca/agent/agent.yaml</literal>
 </para>
 <para>
  Find below a list of the parameters that are supported by
  <phrase>CMM</phrase>.
 </para>
 <para>
  For a description of the available parameters, you can execute the following
  command:
 </para>
<screen>/opt/monasca-agent/bin/monasca-setup --help</screen>
