 <note>
  <para>
   The <literal>dimensions</literal> parameter is not supported by
   <phrase>CMM</phrase>. The installer auto-detects applications and processes
   that are running on your machine and saves the corresponding settings to the
   agent's configuration file. Additional dimensions cannot be specified.
  </para>
